contact_tracing: SES will notify Student Health Services who will work with the Sumter County Health Department to get students connected with a registered case manager who will determine the appropriate course of action such as COVID-19 testing, contact tracing, and/or quarantine and isolation instructions.
self_reporting:
Students who are experiencing symptoms of COVID-19, have tested positive, or have been directly exposed to someone who tested positive:

Do not go to class, or leave class immediately if symptoms begin while in class.
Fill out the COVID-19 Online Report at gsw.edu/COVIDreport or email covid@gsw.edu which will notify the Office of the Vice President for Student Engagement and Success (SES).
